{"word":"γλυφίς","slug":"γλυφίς","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n22420\" key=\"glufi/s\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"suff\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">γλυφ-ίς</orth>, <itype lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"itype\">ίδος</itype>, <gen lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gen\">ἡ</gen>, in early writers always pl. <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">γλυφίδες</foreign> (but sg., opp. <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἀκίς</foreign>, of the constellation Sagitta, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg1431.tlg001:2:5:12\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Hipparch.\">Hipparch.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">2.5.12</biblScope> </bibl>), <sense id=\"n22420.0\" n=\"A\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">notched end</tr_> of the arrow, <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ἕλκε δ᾽ ὁμοῦ γλυφίδας τε λαβὼν καὶ νεῦρα</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:4:122\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Il.\">Il.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">4.122</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ἕλκεν νευρὴν γλυφίδας τε</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:21:419\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Od.\">Od.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">21.419</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">γλυφίδες μέσσῃ ἐγκάτθετο νευρῇ</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0001.tlg001.perseus-grc1:3:282\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ A.R.\">A.R.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">3.282</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; but perh. of <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">notches</tr_> or <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">grooves</tr_> for the fingers, <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">παρὰ τὰς γλυφίδας περιειλίξαντες καὶ πτερώδαντες τὸ βυβλίον</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0016.tlg001.perseus-grc1:8:128\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Hdt.\">Hdt.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">8.128</biblScope></bibl></cit>, cf. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0058.tlg001.perseus-grc1:31:26\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Aen.Tact.</author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">31.26</biblScope> </bibl>; <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">τόξων πτερωταὶ γλυφίδες</foreign>, poet. for <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">the arrow itself</tr_>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0006.tlg016.perseus-grc1:274\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ E.\">E.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Or.\">Or.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">274</biblScope></bibl>, cf. <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <title_ TEIform=\"title\">AP</title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">5.57</biblScope> </bibl> (<bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Arch.\">Arch.</a></author></bibl>, sg.): also in pl., <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">notches in the arrow-head</tr_>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0715.tlg001:6:88\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Paul.Aeg.</author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">6.88</biblScope></bibl>. </sense> <sense n=\"II\" id=\"n22420.1\" level=\"2\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">pen-knife,</tr_> <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">AP</author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">6.62</biblScope> </bibl> (<bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\